Package imagingbook.common.geometry.ellipse

Class AlgebraicEllipse

  • java.lang.Object
    • imagingbook.common.geometry.ellipse.AlgebraicEllipse
  • public class AlgebraicEllipse
extends Object
    Represents an algebraic ellipse with the implicit equation A x^2 + B x y + C y^2 + D x + E y + F = 0. Parameters A, ..., F are normalized such that B^2 - 4 A C = -1. Instances are immutable.
